Class IPForwardingOperationsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.management.network.IPForwardingOperationsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class IPForwardingOperationsImpl
extends Object
implements ServiceOperations<NetworkManagementClientImpl>, IPForwardingOperations
    The Network Management API includes operations for managing the IP Forwarding for your roles and network interfaces in your subscription.
